title: Vadym Yanchak
text:
Vadym Ihorovych Yanchak (; born 7 February 1999) is a <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Oleksandriya">FC Oleksandriya</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Ukrainian%20Second%20League">Ukrainian Second League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Lviv">Lviv</a> on 19 August 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Nyva%20Vinnytsia">Nyva Vinnytsia</a>.
